The singer-songwriter's pop-influenced melodies and quirky, wry lyrics provide a perfect, energetic balance to the lush, sprawling arrangements, while the piano-driven ballads offer healing comfort and yearning, creating a mesmerizing mix of upbeat, playful joy and bittersweet, melancholic longing. Whether you're hanging out with friends, hitting the road for a road trip, or just feeling the urge to let loose and have some fun, this album is the perfect soundtrack to your TGIF, combining the coolncocky attitude of glam rock with the stylish, contemporary pop rock of today.
